Advent o Code
=============

Advent of code (I am going to call it as AOC) an Advent calendar of small programming puzzles created by Eric Wastl.
These puzzles can be solved in any programming language.

I recently came across advent of code and the puzzles really piqued my interest. I decided to solve these puzzles and share my solutions to the world. I enjoy stuff like this and it's fun solving the questions!

My solutions might not be the best or most efficient ones out there, but still, I'm going to share them with the world.

I am going to solve these questions one at a time, program the solutions by hand, in my free time. Looking forward to completing all the AOC puzzles!

Check out: https://adventofcode.com/2025/about
